dc_title_s: LiDAR-Derived Tiled Hydro-Enforced DEM for Clark County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data represents a LiDAR-derived hydro-enforced (breakline) tiled Digital Elevation Model (DEM) for Clark County, Wisconsin in 2018. This dataset contains individual files available for download consisting of smaller tiled geographic areas over the extent of an entire county.
uw_supplemental_s: This data is also available as a series of tiles to enable downloads of smaller, more specific areas within the county. To access the tiled data, please visit: https://www.sco.wisc.edu/scoapps/lidar/tile-search/?layer=clark
